settings.description: Mario goes through the starting area of Bowser's Airship and must defeat boom boom. Bowsers airship 2 is next.
A short level that shows Mario getting past bowsers defenses to his castle, I wonder why it's so weak? Bowser's Castle is Next.
mario finds a fort underground and thwomps can noclip lmao, second level with the trap so mario cant escape boom boom!!!!!!!!!!!!!!1111  testing for future project
Mario finds himself in the Underground Bunker after taking on the air fleet, he must get through it without any mistakes. Or else...
You and your crew are on vacation when a anomaly strikes your ship and you and your crew evacuates! You find your ship safe but 4 of your crewmates are missing! Find them! Based off: VVVVVV
Mario finds himself in a World with water, can he escape to cloud land? Base of operations of M and L are ahead, so be quick!
Mario finds a rest area and stays there to pass some time before he's ready to fight bowser. It seems inside it is testing gizmos. Cloud Land 3 is next.
After Mario gets through Cloud Land 1, he finds an airship and must steal the treasure! Don't die! Cloud Land 2 is next.
Mario Adventures Through the clouds to get to Bowsers Castle, nowhere near yet...
After a "long" adventure, you finally made it! Now you must go through the entire world to get to the final boss, bowser. Take the Hammer suit with you and a few more powerups to defeat him!
You find yourself in an unknown dimension, and you must find your ship. Will you escape, or will you stay here forever?

Fly, slide and spin through the sky and Bowser's castle!
(For Smaghetti Build Contest #2.)
Wendy gets her Airship redesigned, With various Airships added for assistant, Mario goes to the airship by using an mini airship instead of climbing, Good Luck Defeating Wendy & Finding a Secret Exit
Embarking a Journey on the First Unused level but It's Improved by a little bit, Good luck finding the hidden Ace coins!
Dodge the bullets, Touch the snake Corners, and defeat Lemmy, He has more lives and resistance to fire than ever before. Good luck defeating Lemmy and finding the secret exit!
